column5: GOOD LUCK THIS WEEKEND.  REMEMBER TO STOP IN SOUTH RIVER FOR THE PANZO.  AND DONT LISTEN TO WHAT THEY SAY UP THERE YOU WONT LOOK FUNNY IN THE MIDDLE OF THE LAKE WITH YOUR WADERS AND FLOAT ROD
Yes...good luck!  I just know that somehow a steelie will come out of the ice up there....LOL.  Stay safe...the roads may be bad.
